Third-party assets (not covered by the MIT license above)

The audio file Vladimir_Putin_-_Molodec_politik_lider_i_borec_72438381.mp3 is the
track «Молодец, политик, лидер и борец» (Владимир Путин). It was included by the
project authors on their own initiative, without a separate agreement with the
rights holder; attribution is provided in good faith (track title, artist name,
and a public listing URL: https://rus.hitmotop.com/song/72438381). Copyright and
related rights remain with the author and/or their licensees. The file is bundled
for use as the in-game soundtrack; redistribution of the audio may require separate
permission from the rights holder.

